Title: A Barrow Den Burial
Description:
All that is left to do is to gather my sister's remains and bring them to the barrow den. 
 
Please meet me there, $n. I could use a friend.
ObjectivesText: Meet Kelestra outside the barrow den at the Fields of Reverie.
RewardText:
<Kelestra is on the verge of tears.>

They refuse to let me in. After all we have done. They deny my sister peace!
